GridPrint Privacy Policy
Last updated: October 2025

GridPrint is a Chrome extension that allows users to create printable grids of images, supporting A4 and A3 page sizes with PDF export. All processing is done locally on your device.

Data Collection and Usage:
- GridPrint does not collect, store, or transmit any user data.
- Images uploaded by users are processed locally and are not sent to any servers or third parties.
- No personal information is gathered, and no analytics or tracking are used.

Contact:
For questions or feedback, reach out to mrjamesdorey@gmail.com.
